  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT303-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">ceṟippaṟivuṟīi varaivu kaṭāyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Inquiring about marriage [and] informing about
          confinement. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT303">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> kaḻitērn tacaiiya karuṅkāl veṇkuru</l>
          <l> kaṭaikarait tāḻaik kuḻīip peruṅkaṭa</l>
          <l> luṭaitirai yoliyiṟ ṟuñcun tuṟaiva</l>
          <l> toṉṉilai nekiḻnta vaḷaiya ḷīṅkup</l>
          <l> pacantaṉaṇ maṉṉeṉ ṟōḻi yeṉṉoṭu</l>
          <l> miṉṉiṇarp puṉṉaiyam pukarniḻaṟ</l>
          <l> poṉvari yalava ṉāṭṭiya ñāṉṟē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>O man from the ghat, where the black-legged white egrets,</l>
          <l rend="indent">who have come to rest after searching the backwaters, are sleeping</l>
          <l rend="indent3">with the sound of breaking waves from the great sea,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">crowded on the Tāḻai trees on the setting shore,</l>
          <l>she with bangles which have loosened from [their] old state here,</l>
          <l>my friend, became pale indeed,</l>
          <l rend="indent">since she chased golden-striped crabs with me</l>
          <l rend="indent2">in the spotty shade of the Puṉṉai trees with flashing clusters.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
